								<h2>Catholic Centre for Immigrants – Ottawa</h2>
				<div class="excerpt">CCI Ottawa assists newcomers in realizing their full potential in Canadian society. The Catholic Centre for Immigrants promotes and facilitates the reception of newcomers to Canada, and sensitizes the community to address newcomers’ needs and invites it to respond.				<br>
				<a href="http://cciottawa.ca/about-us/mission/" class="more">Read More</a>
				</div>
				
